articles.title: Williams boss James Vowles labels Alex Albon/Logan Sargeant chassis swap situation in Melbourne 'unacceptable in modern day F1' | Formula 1® - Formula 1
articles.description: A frustrated James Vowles has admitted that it’s “unacceptable” that Williams have failed to bring a third chassis to Melbourne, after Alex Albon was forced to take over team mate Logan Sargeant’s FW46.
